
Overview of adj responsible

The adj responsible has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                     
1. (9) responsible -- (worthy of or requiring responsibility or trust; or held accountable; "a responsible adult"; "responsible journalism"; "a responsible position"; "the captain is responsible for the ship's safety"; "the cabinet is responsible to the parliament")
2. (1) responsible, responsible for -- (being the agent or cause; "determined who was the responsible party"; "termites were responsible for the damage")
3. creditworthy, responsible -- (having an acceptable credit rating; "a responsible borrower")
